                        <interp inst="t18650410-488-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with a previous conviction at Dartford, in October, 1864, to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. **—<hi rend="italic">
